places:
    place-braavos:
        name: "Braavos"
        type: free_city
        parent: place-essos
        properties:
            also_known_as: "The Secret City"
        notes: "Greatest and most powerful of the Free Cities. Founded by escaped slaves from Valyria who hid in the lagoons of a remote coastline. The city was kept secret for over a century — the Uncloaking is the holiday celebrating its revelation to the world. Built on a hundred small islands connected by bridges. Dominated by the Titan of Braavos, a massive stone and bronze colossus that straddles the entrance to the lagoon. Home of the Iron Bank of Braavos (the most powerful financial institution in the known world — 'The Iron Bank will have its due'), the Faceless Men and their temple the House of Black and White, the Sealord, and the legendary water dancers (bravos who fight with slender blades). Syrio Forel, Arya's dancing master, was the First Sword of Braavos. The city is deeply anti-slavery — 'No man may take a slave in Braavos.'"
